1837
01:52:11,000 --> 01:52:13,480
Don't even think about it. Don't even try.

1838
01:52:13,720 --> 01:52:16,640
This is us, rolling to Code 2, High,
at Verrina Place.

1839
01:52:16,880 --> 01:52:19,480
Shit. This time
we wait for the bomb squad.

1840
01:52:19,720 --> 01:52:23,560
Do you think I want to end up
in uniform again?

1841
01:55:17,360 --> 01:55:21,160
{y:i}20-William-12,
{y:i}the REA Bomb Squad's en route. All units.

1842
01:55:21,400 --> 01:55:23,800
{y:i}Those guys gonna get in the way again?

1843
01:55:24,040 --> 01:55:25,960
There it is. Happy? Let's go.

1844
01:55:26,200 --> 01:55:28,040
We ain't seen nothing yet, Rog.

1845
01:55:28,280 --> 01:55:30,440
- Get me closer.
- It's roped off.

1846
01:55:30,680 --> 01:55:33,960
- Can't see the bomb squad anywhere.
- They're coming.

1847
01:55:34,200 --> 01:55:36,320
Stop here and I'll just get out.

1848
01:55:36,560 --> 01:55:38,920
No, don't get out of the car, Riggs!

1849
01:55:39,160 --> 01:55:41,320
Tell me, was it the red wire or blue...

1850
01:55:41,560 --> 01:55:43,560
- Let's get out of here.
- Step on the gas.

1851
01:55:43,800 --> 01:55:45,040
They'll never believe this!

1852
01:55:45,280 --> 01:55:47,760
- I hope nobody saw us.
- They'll blame us.

1853
01:55:48,000 --> 01:55:51,080
Let's keep cool. You'd better
get your girdle out of mothballs.

1854
01:55:51,320 --> 01:55:53,480
They'll say, "Back in uniform again."

1855
01:55:53,720 --> 01:55:55,840
Ten more years of this!

1856
01:55:56,080 --> 01:56:00,560
{y:i}I'm too old for this shit.
